import React, {useState} from "react"; import axios from "axios"; //import { useHistory } from "react-router-dom"; // components export default function CardSettings() { const url="http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/criminal-details" const[data,setData]=useState({ criminal_name: "", criminal_age: "", criminal_image: null, status: "", crime_committed: "" }) function submit(e) { e.preventDefault(); axios.post(url,{ criminal_name: data.criminal_name, criminal_age: data.criminal_age, criminal_image: data.criminal_image, status: data.status }) } function handle(e){ const newdata={...data} if(data==="criminal_image"){ newdata[e.target.id]=e.target.files[0] } else{ newdata[e.target.id]=e.target.value } setData(newdata) console.log(newdata) } return ( <>
CRIMINAL DATA
submit(e)}>
Criminal Details
handle(e)} id="criminal_name" value={data.criminal_name} />
handle(e)} id="criminal_age" value={data.criminal_age} />
handle(e)} id="criminal_image" value={data.criminal_image} />
OTHER DETAILS
handle(e)} id="status" value={data.status} />
handle(e)} id="crime_committed" value={data.crime_committed} />
); }
